## Installation

Latest release:

Recommended for beginners, with conda:

```sh
conda install -c conda-forge cartes
```

or with pip:

```sh
pip install cartes
```

Development version, with uv:

```sh
git clone https://github.com/xoolive/cartes
cd cartes
uv sync --dev
```

